            <h3 class="hours_header" id="mm_page_title">Gift Cards</h3>
            <p class="page_desc">
                The Dixie Outlet Mall gift card is the perfect gift for every occasion. Gift cards are available for sale at the Guest Services Desk in any amount from $5 to $500. There is no activation fee.

                <br />
                The Dixie Outlet Mall gift card offers great flexibility of use since it is redeemable at nearly 1,500 participating stores within Cushman & Wakefields’s portfolio of shopping centres. The gift card program is valid at 18 shopping centres in Quebec as well as one in Ontario.
                <br><br>
                <a href="//codecloud.cdn.speedyrails.net/sites/599ed8136e6f647d28200000/application/pdf/1523389364000/DX_CominarGiftCard_FA (1).pdf" target="_blank">Good to the very end: Cominar Gift Cards.</a>
            </p>
            <h5 class="page_miniheads">Card Balance</h5>
            <p class="page_desc">
                To check the balance of your Dixie Outlet Mall gift card, please call 1-800 755-8608, or visit <a target="_blank" href="https://www.getmybalance.com">www.getmybalance.com</a>
            </p>
            
            <div class="margin_10"></div>
